  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "With the determination to stick\nTO their posts night and day for\nthe next two weeks, Misses Clara\nand Dorothy Weathered, Of Mos\ncow. Idaho, have taken front places\nin the line to be formed at the\nOccur d'Alene land Office when a\ntownship on Marble creek is to\nopened for homesteading on Oct.\n30. Four other homesteaders have\njoined them and are now occupying\nchairs at the entrance to the land\nOffice. prepared for the long wait\nIn order to be first to file on the\nland. The property they hope to\nsecure Is covered with valuable\ntimber."
    }
